PrecisRegulations Amending the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (VEHICLE OVERLOADING) which address the problem of overloading the chassis of a vehicle that is customized by someone other than the original manufacturer of the vehicle's main assembly, by specifying the criteria to be considered when determining the "unloaded vehicle mass" and the "vehicle capacity mass".
